{"tid":1994682,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人已經習慣左留喺屋企","createTime":"2020-04-29T15:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T10:12:34.000Z","uid":9667,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e473f17dd15559a8481dd6de7a3fe29a441894","tid":1994682,"uid":9667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:54:01.000Z","msg":"本身冇乜朋友 唔會話特別約出黎食飯行街<br />\n肺炎停課之後 都好少見到班fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為平時都係番學先會見 放學有時一大班食飯 吹下水<br />\n再加上19年年尾同男友分左手 更加少左好多出街機會<br />\n呢排忙下asm 喺屋企上下堂又一日<br />\n慢慢好似習慣左呢種生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但同時得閒嘅時候就喺到諗自己會唔會孤獨一世<br />\n呢種感覺好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16db61d3d638f42770446c17d0dc60b05b39843f","tid":1994682,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:56:11.000Z","msg":"宅係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad606bd81ce7acaafc52f79a566847fdd8c19be","tid":1994682,"uid":222115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:27:21.000Z","msg":"我已經習慣到唔想岀街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3587626090a310e05e7d93b5cbe6117ce83ca217","tid":1994682,"uid":349439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"只要有錢水電煤食物手機遊戲機，我可以摺到天荒地老"},{"pid":"58cb5da92a208cfddc2ab3c29057fbd860f562b1","tid":1994682,"uid":142017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T20:01:56.000Z","msg":"毒開 同平時無咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30774ef0a1c599475b1694cdaf3a4c9adf69185","tid":1994682,"uid":229767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58cb5da92a208cfddc2ab3c29057fbd860f562b1","tid":1994682,"uid":142017,"like":2,